     H            Y.
      ** AB#RFV **********************************************
      *  FORD ROUTE MASTER MAINTENANCE                       *
      *  K.KASHIWAGI 03.05.2001                              *
      ********************************* AB#RFV ***************
      * FIRST SCREEN
      * F3 - EXIT
      * F5 - ADD
      * F7 - CHANGE
      * F9 - DELETE
      *
      * ADD SCREEN
      * F3 - EXIT
      * F5 - ADD
      * F12- PREVIOUS SCREEN
      *
      * CHANGE SCREEN
      * F3 - EXIT
      * F5 - CHANGE
      * F12- PREVIOUS SCREEN
      *
      * DELETE SCREEN
      * F3 - EXIT
      * F5 - DELETE
      * F12- PREVIOUS SCREEN
      *
      * IN99 ERROR
      * IN98 EXECUTION MESSAGE
      ********************************* AB#RFV ***************
     FAB#PWFV CF  E                    WORKSTN
     FABFDP01 UF  E           K        DISK                      A
     FGADPL15 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAGDPL12 IF  E           K        DISK
      *
     E                    MSGTBL  1  12 60
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80QAKYMD
     I                                        1   40QAKOYY
     I                                        5   60QAKOMM
     I                                        7   80QAKODD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80QASYMD
     I                                        1   40QASKYY
     I                                        5   60QASKMM
     I                                        7   80QASKDD
     I* EFFECTIVE DATE FROM ABFDP01
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80QAEYMD
     I                                        1   40QAEFYY
     I                                        5   60QAEFMM
     I                                        7   80QAEFDD
     I* EFFECTIVE DATE FROM AB#PWFV2
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80EYMD2
     I                                        1   40EFYY2
     I                                        5   60EFMM2
     I                                        7   80EFDD2
     I* EFFECTIVE DATE FROM AB#PWFV3
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80EYMD3
     I                                        1   40EFYY3
     I                                        5   60EFMM3
     I                                        7   80EFDD3
     I* EFFECTIVE DATE FROM AB#PWFV4
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80EYMD4
     I                                        1   40EFYY4
     I                                        5   60EFMM4
     I                                        7   80EFDD4
     I* SYSTEM DATE & TIME
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80DATE
     I                                        1   20W@CT
     I                                        3   40W@YY
     I                                        5   60W@MM
     I                                        7   80W@DD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80DATE2
     I                                        1   40W@YY2
     I                                        5   60W@MM2
     I                                        7   80W@DD2
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80KDATE2
     I                                        1   40KW@YY
     I                                        5   60KW@MM
     I                                        7   80KW@DD
     I            DS
     I                                        1  120#TIME
     I                                        1   20W@HH
     I                                        3   40W@MIN
     I                                        5   60W@SS
     C* FOR DELIVERY CODE
     C           KEY1      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           KNONY   40       KEY FOR GADPL13
     C*
     C           KEY2      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           KPLAN   5        KEY FOR ABFDP01
     C                     KFLD           KDOCK   4        KEY FOR ABFDP01
     C* FOR EFFECTIVE DATE
     C           KEY3      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           F8KAYY  40       KEY FOR AGDPL12
     C                     KFLD           F8KAMM  20       KEY FOR AGDPL12
     C                     KFLD           F8KADD  20       KEY FOR AGDPL12
     C* FOR UPDATE PROFILE
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           US     10
     C*
      *--------------*
      * MAIN ROUTINE *
      *--------------*
     C                     EXSR @INTR
     C           W@ID      DOWNE'99'
     C           W@ID      CASEQ'01'      @DSP1            1ST SCREEN
     C           W@ID      CASEQ'02'      @DSP2            ADD SCREEN
     C           W@ID      CASEQ'03'      @DSP3            CHG SCREEN
     C           W@ID      CASEQ'04'      @DSP4            DELETE SCREEN
     C                     ENDCS
     C                     ENDDO
     C*
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
     C*
      *---------------*
      * INITIALIZATION
      *---------------*
     C           @INTR     BEGSR
     C                     MOVEL'01'      W@ID    2
     C                     TIME           #TIME
     C                     MOVE *DATE     DATE
     C                     Z-ADD2000      W@YY4   40
     C                     ADD  W@YY      W@YY4
     C                     SETOF                     9998
     C                     ENDSR
      *--------------*
      * FIRST SCREEN *
      *--------------*
     C           @DSP1     BEGSR
     C                     EXFMTAB#PWFV1
     C                     MOVEL*BLANKS   @MSG1
     C                     SETOF                     993098
     C                     SETOF                     31
      *
      * F3=EXIT IS PRESSED
      *
     C                     SELEC
     C           *INKC     WHEQ '1'
     C                     MOVEL'99'      W@ID
      *
      * F5=ADD IS PRESSED
      *
     C           *INKE     WHEQ '1'
     C                     EXSR @CHK1
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '0'
     C                     CLEARAB#PWFV2
     C                     MOVELPLAN1     PLAN2
     C                     MOVELDOCK1     DOCK2
     C                     MOVEL'02'      W@ID
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * F7=CHANGE IS PRESSED
      *
     C           *INKG     WHEQ '1'
     C                     EXSR @CHK2
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '0'
     C                     CLEARAB#PWFV3
     C                     MOVELPLAN1     PLAN3
     C                     MOVELDOCK1     DOCK3
     C                     Z-ADDQANONY    NONY3
     C                     MOVELQAROUT    ROUT3
     C                     MOVELQAMODE    MODE3
     C                     MOVELQASCAC    SCAC3
     C                     Z-ADDQAEYMD    EYMD3
     C                     MOVEL'03'      W@ID
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * F9=DELETE IS PRESSED
      *
     C           *INKI     WHEQ '1'
     C                     EXSR @CHK2
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '0'
     C                     CLEARAB#PWFV4
     C                     MOVELPLAN1     PLAN4
     C                     MOVELDOCK1     DOCK4
     C                     Z-ADDQANONY    NONY4
     C                     MOVELQAROUT    ROUT4
     C                     MOVELQAMODE    MODE4
     C                     MOVELQASCAC    SCAC4
     C                     Z-ADDQAEYMD    EYMD4
     C                     MOVEL'04'      W@ID
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     OTHER
      *
      * ENTER KEY IS PRESSED
      *
     C           PLAN1     IFEQ *BLANKS
     C                     SETON                     3099
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,4  @MSG1
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSL
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *--------------------*
     C* CHK1 FOR ADD RECORD
      *--------------------*
     C           @CHK1     BEGSR
     C*
     C           PLAN1     IFEQ *BLANKS
     C                     SETON                     3099
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,4  @MSG1
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * CHECK IF THE RECORD ALREADY EXISTS OR NOT WHEN NO ERROR
      *
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '0'
     C                     MOVELPLAN1     KPLAN
     C                     MOVELDOCK1     KDOCK
     C                     SETOF                     70
     C           KEY2      CHAINABFDP01R             70
     C           *IN70     IFEQ '0'
     C           QASKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C           QASYMD    ANDLE*DATE
     C                     ELSE
     C                     SETON                     993031
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,2  @MSG1
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDSR
     C*
      *-------------------------------*
     C* CHK2 FOR CHAGE OR DELETE RECORD
      *-------------------------------*
     C           @CHK2     BEGSR
     C           PLAN1     IFEQ *BLANKS
     C                     SETON                     9930
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,4  @MSG1
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * CHECK IF THE RECORD ALREADY EXISTS OR NOT WHEN NO ERROR
      *
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '0'
     C                     MOVELPLAN1     KPLAN
     C                     MOVELDOCK1     KDOCK
     C                     SETOF                     70
     C           KEY2      CHAINABFDP01R             70
     C           *IN70     IFEQ '1'
     C                     SETON                     993031
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,3  @MSG1
     C                     ELSE
     C           QASKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C           QASYMD    ANDLE*DATE
     C                     SETON                     993031
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,3  @MSG1
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDSR
      *---------------*
      * ADD SCREEN *
      *---------------*
     C           @DSP2     BEGSR
     C                     EXFMTAB#PWFV2
     C                     MOVEL*BLANKS   @MSG2
     C                     SETOF                     993233
     C                     SETOF                     343536
     C                     SETOF                     70
     C*
     C                     SELEC
     C* F3=EXIT
     C           *INKC     WHEQ '1'
     C                     MOVEL'99'      W@ID
     C* F12=PREVIOUS
     C           *INKL     WHEQ '1'
     C                     CLEARAB#PWFV1
     C                     MOVEL'01'      W@ID
     C* F5=ADD
     C           *INKE     WHEQ '1'
     C                     EXSR @ADCHK
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '0'
     C                     EXSR @WRT
     C                     CLEARAB#PWFV1
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,10 @MSG1
     C                     SETON                     98
     C                     MOVEL'01'      W@ID
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C                     OTHER
     C                     EXSR @ADCHK
     C                     ENDSL
     C*
     C                     ENDSR
      *---------------*
      * WRITE RTN     *
      *---------------*
     C           @WRT      BEGSR
  KK C                     SETOF                     70
     C           KEY2      CHAINABFDP01R             70
     C                     Z-ADD0         QASYMD
     C                     Z-ADDNONY2     QANONY
     C                     MOVELPLAN2     QAPLAN
     C                     MOVELDOCK2     QADOCK
     C                     MOVELROUT2     QAROUT
     C                     MOVELMODE2     QAMODE
     C                     MOVELSCAC2     QASCAC
     C                     Z-ADDEYMD2     QAEYMD
     C                     Z-ADDW@YY      W@YY2
     C                     Z-ADDW@MM      W@MM2
     C                     Z-ADDW@DD      W@DD2
     C                     ADD  20000000  DATE2
     C                     MOVE DATE2     QAKYMD
     C                     TIME           #TIME
     C                     Z-ADDW@HH      QAKOHH
     C                     Z-ADDW@MIN     QAKOSS
     C                     MOVELUS        QAKOME
  KK C           *IN70     IFEQ '0'
     C                     MOVEL*BLANKS   QASKJY
     C                     Z-ADD0         QASYMD
     C                     UPDATABFDP01R
     C                     ELSE
     C                     WRITEABFDP01R
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDSR
     C*-------
     C* CHANGE
     C*-------
     C           @DSP3     BEGSR
     C                     EXFMTAB#PWFV3
     C                     MOVEL*BLANKS   @MSG3
     C                     SETOF                     993233
     C                     SETOF                     343536
     C                     SETOF                     70
     C*
     C                     SELEC
     C* F3=EXIT
     C           *INKC     WHEQ '1'
     C                     MOVEL'99'      W@ID
     C* F12=PREVIOUS
     C           *INKL     WHEQ '1'
     C                     CLEARAB#PWFV1
     C                     MOVEL'01'      W@ID
     C* F5=CHANGE
     C           *INKE     WHEQ '1'
     C                     EXSR @CHCHK
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '0'
 KK  C           *IN70     ANDEQ'0'
     C                     Z-ADDNONY3     QANONY
     C                     MOVELPLAN3     QAPLAN
     C                     MOVELDOCK3     QADOCK
     C                     MOVELROUT3     QAROUT
     C                     MOVELMODE3     QAMODE
     C                     MOVELSCAC3     QASCAC
     C                     Z-ADDEYMD3     QAEYMD
     C                     Z-ADDW@YY      W@YY2
     C                     Z-ADDW@MM      W@MM2
     C                     Z-ADDW@DD      W@DD2
     C                     ADD  20000000  DATE2
     C                     MOVE DATE2     QAKYMD
     C                     TIME           #TIME
     C                     Z-ADDW@HH      QAKOHH
     C                     Z-ADDW@MIN     QAKOSS
     C                     MOVELUS        QAKOME
     C                     UPDATABFDP01R
     C                     CLEARAB#PWFV1
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,11 @MSG1
     C                     SETON                     98
     C                     MOVEL'01'      W@ID
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C                     OTHER
     C                     EXSR @CHCHK
     C                     ENDSL
     C*
     C                     ENDSR
     C*--------
     C* DELETE
     C*--------
     C           @DSP4     BEGSR
     C                     EXFMTAB#PWFV4
     C                     MOVEL*BLANKS   @MSG4
     C* F3=EXIT
     C                     SELEC
     C           *INKC     WHEQ '1'
     C                     MOVEL'99'      W@ID
     C* F12=PREVIOUS
     C           *INKL     WHEQ '1'
     C                     CLEARAB#PWFV1
     C                     MOVEL'01'      W@ID
     C* F5=DELETE
     C           *INKE     WHEQ '1'
 KK  C           *IN70     ANDEQ'0'
     C                     MOVEL'D'       QASKJY
     C                     Z-ADDW@YY      W@YY2
     C                     Z-ADDW@MM      W@MM2
     C                     Z-ADDW@DD      W@DD2
     C                     ADD  20000000  DATE2
     C                     MOVE DATE2     QASYMD
     C                     MOVE DATE2     QAKYMD
     C                     TIME           #TIME
     C                     Z-ADDW@HH      QAKOHH
     C                     Z-ADDW@MIN     QAKOSS
     C                     MOVELUS        QAKOME
     C                     UPDATABFDP01R
     C                     CLEARAB#PWFV1
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,12 @MSG1
     C                     SETON                     98
     C                     MOVEL'01'      W@ID
     C*
     C                     ENDSL
     C*
     C                     ENDSR
     C*--------------
     C* ADD CHECK
     C*--------------
     C           @ADCHK    BEGSR
     C* DELIVERY CODE CHECK
     C           NONY2     IFEQ 0
     C                     SETON                     9932
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,1  @MSG2
     C                     ELSE
     C                     Z-ADDNONY2     KNONY
     C                     SETOF                     70
     C           KEY1      CHAINGADPL15              70
     C           *IN70     IFEQ '1'
     C                     SETON                     9932
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,1  @MSG2
     C                     ELSE
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C* ROUTE CHECK
     C           ROUT2     IFEQ *BLANKS
     C                     SETON                     33
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '0'
     C                     SETON                     99
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,6  @MSG2
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C* MODE CHECK
     C           MODE2     IFEQ *BLANKS
     C                     SETON                     34
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '0'
     C                     SETON                     99
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,7  @MSG2
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C* SCAC CHECK
     C           SCAC2     IFEQ *BLANKS
     C                     SETON                     35
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '0'
     C                     SETON                     99
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,8  @MSG2
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C* EFFECTIVE DATE CHECK
     C                     Z-ADDEFYY2     F8KAYY
     C                     Z-ADDEFMM2     F8KAMM
     C                     Z-ADDEFDD2     F8KADD
     C                     SETOF                     80
     C           KEY3      CHAINAGDPL12              80    CALENDAR FILE
     C           *IN80     IFEQ '1'
     C                     SETON                     36
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '0'
     C                     SETON                     99
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,9  @MSG2
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C                     ENDSR
     C*--------------
     C* CHG CHECK
     C*--------------
     C           @CHCHK    BEGSR
     C* DELIVERY CODE CHECK
     C           NONY3     IFEQ 0
     C                     SETON                     9932
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,1  @MSG3
     C                     ELSE
     C                     Z-ADDNONY3     KNONY
     C                     SETOF                     70
     C           KEY1      CHAINGADPL15              70
     C           *IN70     IFEQ '1'
     C                     SETON                     9932
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,1  @MSG3
     C                     ELSE
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C* ROUTE CHECK
     C           ROUT3     IFEQ *BLANKS
     C                     SETON                     33
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '0'
     C                     SETON                     99
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,6  @MSG3
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C* MODE CHECK
     C           MODE3     IFEQ *BLANKS
     C                     SETON                     34
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '0'
     C                     SETON                     99
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,7  @MSG3
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C* SCAC CHECK
     C           SCAC3     IFEQ *BLANKS
     C                     SETON                     35
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '0'
     C                     SETON                     99
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,8  @MSG3
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C* EFFECTIVE DATE CHECK
     C                     Z-ADDEFYY3     F8KAYY
     C                     Z-ADDEFMM3     F8KAMM
     C                     Z-ADDEFDD3     F8KADD
     C                     SETOF                     80
     C           KEY3      CHAINAGDPL12              80    CALENDAR FILE
     C           *IN80     IFEQ '1'
     C                     SETON                     36
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '0'
     C                     SETON                     99
     C                     MOVELMSGTBL,9  @MSG3
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C                     ENDSR
** (MSGTBL)
E-01 INVALID DELIVERY CODE.
E-02 RECORD ALREADY EXISTS.
E-03 RECORD DOES NOT EXIST.
E-04 INVALID PLANT CODE.
E-05 INVALID DOCK.
E-06 INVALID ROUTE CODE.
E-07 INVALID MODE CODE.
E-08 INVALID SCAC CODE.
E-09 INVALID EFFECTIVE DATE.
E-10 PROCESS FOR ADDING RECORD IS COMPLETED.
E-11 PROCESS FOR CHANGE RECORD IS COMPLETED.
E-12 PROCESS FOR DELETE RECORD IS COMPLETED.
